  "title": "Drug/supplement interaction pairs",
  "description": "Baked drug-/supplement-interaction dataset (issue #144) — flags known interactions between two ACTIVE items in a profile's supplement + medication stack. CURATED HIGH-VALUE SUBSET, not exhaustive; facts from public-domain FDA/DailyMed labeling, NIH MedlinePlus/ODS/NCCIH, RxNorm (all public domain). INFORMATIONAL, never prescriptive — absence of a flag does NOT mean safe. Committed + HUMAN-REVIEWABLE; regenerate with `npm run gen:interactions`.",
